00:40:26,860 --> 00:40:28,420
But we have to remind her

1086
00:40:28,420 --> 00:40:29,660
that she's just a bridesmaid.

1087
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:31,980
What if she gets infuriated
during the wedding?

1088
00:40:32,380 --> 00:40:32,980
Yeah.

1089
00:40:33,620 --> 00:40:35,340
What should we do if she causes trouble

1090
00:40:35,340 --> 00:40:36,100
during our wedding?

1091
00:40:36,240 --> 00:40:37,180
There's nothing to worry about.

1092
00:40:37,180 --> 00:40:38,300
I'm here, aren't I?

1093
00:40:38,500 --> 00:40:39,860
I can do what Meiqi can do.

1094
00:40:39,860 --> 00:40:41,700
I can even do what she cannot.

1095
00:40:41,700 --> 00:40:43,220
Stop fanning the flames.

1096
00:40:43,220 --> 00:40:44,380
I'm not.

1097
00:40:44,380 --> 00:40:45,980
I'm just making a statement here.

1098
00:40:50,020 --> 00:40:50,660
Hu Gang.

1099
00:40:51,020 --> 00:40:52,540
All clear at Nanxi Hotel.

1100
00:40:52,540 --> 00:40:53,680
Come as soon as possible.

1101
00:40:55,620 --> 00:40:56,220
Who?

1102
00:40:56,820 --> 00:40:57,540
Hu Gang?

1103
00:41:00,560 --> 00:41:01,060
You two...

1104
00:41:01,660 --> 00:41:02,980
That's right. It's us now.

1105
00:41:06,020 --> 00:41:06,540
Meiqi,

1106
00:41:06,860 --> 00:41:07,980
I sent you the marketing plan

1107
00:41:07,980 --> 00:41:09,980
from last Thanksgiving.

1108
00:41:10,220 --> 00:41:12,380
Modify it and make one
for this year's Thanksgiving.

1109
00:41:12,740 --> 00:41:14,060
You have to be detailed.

1110
00:41:14,100 --> 00:41:15,700
Do it immediately. I need it urgently.

1111
00:41:16,660 --> 00:41:17,860
Got it, Samantha.

1112
00:41:31,420 --> 00:41:33,820
It seems Mr. Hu doesn't have the guts
to refuse me after all.

1113
00:41:37,820 --> 00:41:38,500
Mr. Hu,

1114
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:39,380
I think it's fixed.

1115
00:41:39,380 --> 00:41:40,140
Is there sound now?

1116
00:41:40,140 --> 00:41:41,950
Hear it and
see if there's any static noise.

1117
00:41:42,260 --> 00:41:43,140
Nope.

1118
00:41:43,140 --> 00:41:43,940
Nope, huh?

1119
00:41:47,060 --> 00:41:47,660
All done.

1120
00:41:49,380 --> 00:41:49,980
Mr. Hu,

1121
00:41:49,980 --> 00:41:51,180
thank you for coming today.

1122
00:41:51,180 --> 00:41:52,060
You're such a professional.

1123
00:41:52,060 --> 00:41:53,220
Even the technicians

1124
00:41:53,220 --> 00:41:54,380
might not be able to fix this.

1125
00:41:55,060 --> 00:41:56,940
This is an issue with
the transmission cable.

1126
00:41:56,940 --> 00:41:59,420
It's because the console
is too far away from the sound system.

1127
00:41:59,420 --> 00:42:00,740
It'll be fine once you change it

1128
00:42:00,740 --> 00:42:01,550
to a balanced input.

1129
00:42:02,180 --> 00:42:02,980
Thank you, Mr. Hu.

1130
00:42:03,340 --> 00:42:05,540
Not only is Mr. Hu intelligent,

1131
00:42:05,540 --> 00:42:07,140
but he's also very handy.

1132
00:42:07,320 --> 00:42:08,860
Here. A preserved plum as your reward.

1133
00:42:09,900 --> 00:42:10,660
It's your reward.

1134
00:42:10,980 --> 00:42:11,660
Isn't it sweet?

1135
00:42:13,340 --> 00:42:13,860
It is.

1136
00:42:13,860 --> 00:42:14,420
Isn't it?

1137
00:42:15,980 --> 00:42:18,180
Did Mr. Hu have a relationship
with Meiqi before this?

1138
00:42:18,900 --> 00:42:20,380
That's already in the past.

1139
00:42:21,260 --> 00:42:22,620
How did we end up with a love triangle

1140
00:42:22,620 --> 00:42:24,180
on our wedding rehearsal?

1141
00:42:24,180 --> 00:42:25,100
How should I know?

1142
00:42:29,900 --> 00:42:30,460
Hu Gang,

1143
00:42:30,620 --> 00:42:31,660
our home Wi-Fi is down.

1144
00:42:31,860 --> 00:42:33,540
Our Al home system has collapsed.

1145
00:42:33,980 --> 00:42:35,100
Please come and fix it.

1146
00:42:38,340 --> 00:42:39,140
That shouldn't be.

1147
00:42:39,780 --> 00:42:41,660
I installed their Wi-Fi for them.

1148
00:42:41,660 --> 00:42:42,660
It shouldn't be possible.

1149
00:42:55,100 --> 00:42:56,950
The world is noisy

1150
00:42:57,550 --> 00:42:59,930
Turning around,
it's already a distant view

1151
00:43:01,350 --> 00:43:03,230
Once I didnt know what to do

1152
00:43:03,230 --> 00:43:05,310
What to hold quietly

1153
00:43:05,310 --> 00:43:08,260
Like a silent care

1154
00:43:10,120 --> 00:43:12,530
Seasons pass by

1155
00:43:12,530 --> 00:43:15,390
Time ticks away

1156
00:43:15,880 --> 00:43:17,790
Seems like I understand a little

1157
00:43:17,790 --> 00:43:19,570
And also let go of some things

1158
00:43:19,570 --> 00:43:24,290
All the bittersweet flavors
are the essence of youth

1159
00:43:24,290 --> 00:43:27,780
A long letter is written down

1160
00:43:27,930 --> 00:43:31,410
Gently spreading love

1161
00:43:31,610 --> 00:43:35,600
To all the forks in fate

1162
00:43:35,600 --> 00:43:41,230
Loving all the moments
that deserve to be loved
